  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK461">
<l>aḻivatūu māvatūu māki vaḻipayakku</l>
<l>mūtiyamuñ cūḻntu ceyal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let a man reflect on what will be lost, what will be acquired and (from these) what will be his ultimate gain, and (then, let him) act.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
  </text>
